Class Vertex

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.wsu.KepheraSimulator.Vertex
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Vertex
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class defines a drawable object. The basic members and operations could be used to define class(es) for world objects. A more extensive definition could be used for a robot.
